@TomAugspurger can you check that?  If I go to http://pandas.pydata.org/Pandas_Cheat_Sheet.pdf, I'm seeing the old version.  You can tell by looking in two places:

1. On the left side, right above "Create DataFrame with a MultiIndex", there should be two right parens.
2. The last regex on the right side should have one single quote, not two.
